---

<BaseLayout
  title="Über uns - Pixformance"
  description="Etabliertes Markt-Know-How trifft Start-up-Dynamik. Unermüdliche Innovationskraft seit 2012."
>
  <HeaderWithDropdown slot="header" position="sticky">
    <PixformanceLogo slot="logo" />
  </HeaderWithDropdown>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6BDBD1]/10 to-[#86C9BC]/10 overflow-hidden py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center space-y-5">
        <div class="inline-block hero-animate" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#8B1E81]/10 border border-[#8B1E81]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#8B1E81]">
            <Icon name="users" size="sm" />
            Über uns
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight hero-animate" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
          Etabliertes Markt-Know-How trifft
          <span class="text-[#8B1E81]"> Start-up-Dynamik</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-foreground-muted leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto hero-animate" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
          Unermüdliche Innovationskraft – und das bereits seit 2012
        </p>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          {stats.map((stat, index) => (
            <div class="group space-y-2 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white hover:bg-[#8B1E81]/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer hero-animate shadow-lg" style={`animation-delay: ${0.4 + index * 0.1}s;`}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto rounded-xl bg-[#8B1E81] flex items-center justify-center mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-300">
                <Icon name={stat.icon} size="md" class="text-white" />
              </div>
              <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#8B1E81] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                {stat.value}
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-foreground-muted">{stat.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-scroll="fade-up">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#8B1E81]/10 border border-[#8B1E81]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#8B1E81] mb-6">
            <Icon name="building" size="sm" />
            Unser Unternehmen
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
            Pioniere der digitalen Bewegungsanalyse
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-foreground-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Pixformance wurde 2012 gegründet und ist der Pionier in der digitalen Bewegungsanalyse
            und Echtzeit-Feedback. Unter der Leitung von CEO <span class="font-bold text-[#8B1E81]">Valerie Bures-Bönström</span>
            haben wir uns zum führenden Anbieter für digitale Trainingsgeräte in der DACH-Region entwickelt.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unsere patentierte Technologie revolutioniert die Art und Weise, wie Menschen trainieren.
            Mit über <span class="font-bold text-[#8B1E81]">600 Installationen weltweit</span> und mehr als
            <span class="font-bold text-[#8B1E81]">450.000 Trainierenden</span> setzen wir neue Maßstäbe in
            Physiotherapie, Klinik, Fitness und betrieblichem Gesundheitsmanagement.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unser interdisziplinäres Team verbindet technologische Exzellenz mit tiefem Verständnis
            für die Bedürfnisse unserer Kunden. Wir arbeiten kontinuierlich daran, die beste
            Technologie für digitale Bewegungsanalyse bereitzustellen und damit Gesundheits- und
            Fitnessexperten zu befähigen, ihr volles Potential zu verwirklichen.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Management Board Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12" data-scroll="fade-up">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#8B1E81]/10 border border-[#8B1E81]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#8B1E81] mb-6">
          <Icon name="star" size="sm" />
          Geschäftsführung
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          Unser Management Board
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {managementBoard.map((member, index) => (
          <Card
            variant="elevated"
            padding="none"
            class="overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:scale-105 group bg-white"
            data-scroll="scale"
            data-delay={index + 1}
          >
            <div class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent z-10 group-hover:from-[#8B1E81]/80 transition-all duration-500"></div>
              <img
                src={member.image}
                alt={member.name}
                class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />

              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6 z-20">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                  {member.name}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white/90 text-sm font-semibold">
                  {member.role}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12" data-scroll="fade-up">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#8B1E81]/10 border border-[#8B1E81]/20 text-sm font-bold text-[#8B1E81] mb-6">
          <Icon name="users" size="sm" />
          Unser Team
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          Die Menschen hinter Pixformance
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {team.map((member, index) => (
          <Card
            variant="elevated"
            padding="none"
            class="overflow-hidden hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-3 hover:scale-105 group bg-white"
            data-scroll="scale"
            data-delay={Math.min(index + 1, 6)}
          >
            <div class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent z-10 group-hover:from-[#6BDBD1]/80 transition-all duration-500"></div>
              <img
                src={member.image}
                alt={member.name}
                class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />

              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6 z-20">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-white mb-1 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300">
                  {member.name}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white/90 text-sm font-semibold">
                  {member.role}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#8B1E81] via-[#4A3D91] to-[#02308C]"></div>

    <div class="container relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8" data-scroll="fade-up">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
          Werden Sie Teil unserer Erfolgsgeschichte
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Kontaktieren Sie uns für eine unverbindliche Beratung und erfahren Sie,
          wie Pixformance Ihr Unternehmen revolutionieren kann.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center pt-4">
          <Button
            size="lg"
            href="/testen"
            class="bg-white text-[#8B1E81] hover:bg-gray-100"
          >
            Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen
            <Icon name="arrow-right" size="sm" />
          </Button>
          <Button
            size="lg"
            variant="outline"
            href="/konzept"
            class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#8B1E81]"
          >
            Unser Konzept entdecken
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Entry Animation */
  @keyframes hero-entry {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .hero-animate {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: hero-entry 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  /* Scroll Animation Styles */
  [data-scroll] {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  [data-scroll].is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Fade In Up */
  [data-scroll="fade-up"] {
    transform: translateY(30px);
  }

  [data-scroll="fade-up"].is-visible {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Scale In */
  [data-scroll="scale"] {
    transform: scale(0.9);
  }

  [data-scroll="scale"].is-visible {
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  /* Stagger delays */
  [data-scroll][data-delay="1"] {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  [data-scroll][data-delay="2"] {
    transition-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  [data-scroll][data-delay="3"] {
    transition-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  [data-scroll][data-delay="4"] {
    transition-delay: 0.4s;
  }

  [data-scroll][data-delay="5"] {
    transition-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  [data-scroll][data-delay="6"] {
    transition-delay: 0.6s;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Intersection Observer for scroll animations
  const observerOptions = {
    threshold: 0.1,
    rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
  };

  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
      }
    });
  }, observerOptions);

  // Observe all elements with data-scroll attribute
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-scroll]').forEach((el) => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
